Package: mcstprules
Type: Package
Title: Cost Allocation Rules in Minimum Cost Spanning Tree Problems
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Lucía", "Souto Vázquez", 
           email = "luciasouvaz@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computes, analyzes, and visualizes cost allocation rules for 
    Minimum Cost Spanning Tree Problems (MCSTP). The package implements 
    both algorithmic methods and rules based on cooperative game theory, 
    alongside a comprehensive suite of analytical tools to evaluate core 
    stability, geometric properties, and cost sensitivity.
